About Me

I am a provisionally licensed mental health clinician in the Omaha area. In 2012, I earned a Bachelor of Arts in Psychology with a minor in Child, Youth, and Family from the University of Nebraska- Lincoln. In 2018, I graduated from an accredited program at the University of Nebraska- Omaha with a Master of Science in Clinical Mental Health Counseling.
